channel.title: The Hit List
channel.desc: Time for the stars to shine in a celebrity special! The famous faces joining Rochelle and Marvin Humes in this addictively play along music quiz are presenter Pete Wicks and reality star Tasha Ghouri, comedy queens Sian Gibson and Sarah Hadland, and journalist Krishnan Guru-Murthy and dancer Lauren Oakley - who will get the chance to win ?10,000 for their chosen charity?
